{{#is_alert}}

## What's happening?
The NiFi instance on {{host.name}} has failed consecutive connectivity checks.

All NiFi metrics have stopped flowing. Verify that:
- The NiFi process is running
- The API URL is reachable from the Agent host
- Credentials have not expired or been rotated

{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_recovery}}
NiFi connectivity has been restored on {{host.name}}.
{{/is_recovery}}
